"The castle sat on a hill. While it was easy to see, no one could reach it. I know becuase Ive been stuck here alone for six years. I tried to escape once, but I was (obviously) unsuccessful. The oddest part of my current situation is that while there are no other people around, something is keeping me here. When I try to leave, I end up back in the throne room, staring out the window at the mountains beyond the valley. What was so special about this room that whatever this magic is it keeps bringing me here? "